result.formatted_address: 7 Bristol Ave, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: Urban Coffee Roaster

reviews.text:
I'm staying at the Holiday Inn. Went on the hunt for a coffee in the morning. Found a Starbucks.... I was desperate... Then I notice A single ray of sun lite across the street, the Urban Coffee Roaster! 

They nailed it. Every shot is a double. Skilled hands behind the machine. Silky smooth milk. Sign me up twice I'm in.
Great environment to kick back with friends and drink good coffee.   Very rustic and almost anti-establishment.  Being right across from Starbucks makes it easy to find.

5/5 rate are for coffee shops that for me are remarkable and one wouldn't mind the travel time just to get a cup of their coffee and food. Quality of coffee is on my top list whenever I try a new place but let's not forget the environment and people behind it. I believe that great coffee experience would be awesomely great if baristas and staff will connect with you and Urban Coffee Roaster has this! Cool baristas and staff, great food, great coffee! I love the industrial to rustic interior design ( clean and simple), the welcoming environment, plus they accept visa/MasterCard which I find very convenient for those who don't bring cash like me! 😂 will definitely come back here!

Great coffee and brunch. The cold brew has amazing flavours and the menu includes food options that can be made gluten free. 
The staff are all very friendly and helpful. 
Highly recommended as a way to escape the craziness of Hong Kong!!
Great coffee and food. Intriguing industrial style decor. Like Bourke St Bakery (Sydney) but in HK. Small intimate place to get away from the hustle and bustle

result.formatted_address: 香港尖沙咀碧仙桃路7號
result.name: Urban Coffee Roaster

reviews.text:
星期日同個朋友出尖沙咀食lunch聚下舊，食完lunch都未傾完，咁梗係再揾下場，可以坐底再慢慢傾啦😂

呢間coffee shop係K11附近，舖頭細細，好適合大家坐底吹水，不過環境比較嘈，如果想傾下心事就差啲...但是店內環境絕對係一間幾適合打卡的舖頭。我地由4點幾5點坐到6點半左右，傍晚時份舖頭會熄燈，因為每張枱都有點一個小蠟燭，舖內變得昏暗但又帶著點點黃色的燭光，即刻變得好情調🥰🥰🥰

係咖啡店，咖啡當然係主角啦！！！所以我地2個人，一人叫左一杯咖啡,我就叫左杯Mocha。另外再叫左一件豆腐慕絲芝士蛋糕share食

我杯Mocha好好味😋
另外，特別要讚個豆腐慕絲芝士蛋糕，好滑、好軟棉棉，味道好清淡但好好味，食完都唔滯

I'm staying at the Holiday Inn. Went on the hunt for a coffee in the morning. Found a Starbucks.... I was desperate... Then I notice A single ray of sun lite across the street, the Urban Coffee Roaster! 

They nailed it. Every shot is a double. Skilled hands behind the machine. Silky smooth milk. Sign me up twice I'm in.

2019.05.16

Gesha 1931@Urban Coffee Roaster at Tsim Sha Tsui

Ethiopia Gesha Village Coffee Estate
Narsha Block Gesha 1931 
2018 Auction Lot GVA. 05

Cupping Notes 有 Orange Blossom、
Bergamot、Mandarin Orange，
算是 Citrus 家族吧~

端上桌，嘩，要品酒嗎？

咖啡師：“小的溫度剛好，請先喝。大的溫度高，可以稍等。”

水洗，但甜度絶不失禮。

非常柔和，檸檬微酸、橘子清甜融洽，
聯手按摩口腔，舒服。

放涼，檸檬稍增，質感更厚。

店不大，金屬玻璃白色趟門，raw 地板，
鐵架木椅，就在 K11 Starbucks 對面。

尖沙咀碧仙桃路7號

#尖沙咀咖啡店
#香港咖啡店
#香港
#咖啡
食物味道不錯，但份量偏小，員工好似不是去上班，像去和朋友聊天，玩樂，或許香港的素質就是這樣。

result.name: Urban Coffee Roaster at Galleon

reviews.text: I knew that there is science and wisdom beyond coffee. These guys can demonstrate it! They serve delicious coffee and if you ask them, they might tell you all about it. The vegan chocolate brownie is good but you could skip on cheesecake in my opinion.

Tried the food recently.  Fries is consistently good.  The soy cake tastes fresh, not too sweet, that goes well with dripped coffee.

I don’t remember the name of the coffee I had but it tastes and smells quite differently when it cools down and the temperature changes.  Interesting!

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * 

Newly opened in CWB!
Quality of coffee is as good as its other stores.
Quiet place for coffee, work and reading.
Should try the food another time.

Too late for food on my first visit, too early on my second and finally got the right timing on my third.  Coffee here is really good but it's their uni pasta and soft shell crab donburi that got me visiting 3 times in 3 days. Tuck away in a charming corner of causeway bay, it's quiet but lively... thanks to the excellent crew that runs the place. They care more about you than what they are offering. 👍👍👍
This is a brilliant cafe, so well run and the food coffee and tea and products for sale are so good, topping most cafes in Hong Kong.  Not wheelchair or stroller accessible

This coffee shop is located at the upper floor of a homemaking / furniture store. The concept is pretty cute. Though food options like most furniture-store-coffee-shop tagalong, are limited. If you opt for a light lunch/dinner, it’s a good place.

要搵真係唔容易

首先叫咗個炸單骨雞翼♥️
配芥末沙律醬正啊
呢個海膽闊麵都好正
海膽味好香濃
海膽亦好鮮甜

朋友揀咗呢個漢堡扒飯
漢堡扒好厚好嫩滑
牛肉味重

豆腐芝士蛋糕
味道幾好

焦糖布丁🍮
好香焦糖好正
上面嘅脆脆拎嚟點cream一流

呢度嘅環境好舒服😌
仲有酒類可以叫
好正♥️
野食亦都好味
性價比高

服務亦好好啊
侍應好貼心

下次再嚟試下佢個松葉蟹肉飯先🦀
不過好可惜嘅係我唔飲得咖啡
